sqlViews.name: MAL - Sub-national data file uploaded to WMR Form
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
Select
  organisationunit.code,
  organisationunit.uid,
  organisationunit.organisationunitid As OrgId,
  organisationunit.name As OrgName,
  datavalue.value
From
  datavalue Inner Join
  organisationunit On datavalue.sourceid =
    organisationunit.organisationunitid
Where
  datavalue.dataelementid in (SELECT dataelementid FROM dataelement wHERE uid='c9p5aky1SCy') And
  datavalue.periodid = (SELECT periodid FROM period WHERE periodtypeid=8 AND eXTRACT(YEAR from startdate) = 2019 and eXTRACT(YEAR from enddate) = 2019)
Order By
  organisationunit.code
sqlViews.displayName: Sub-national data file uploaded to WMR Form
sqlViews.description: Sub-national data file uploaded to WMR Form

sqlViews.name: MAL - Countries datavalues lastest update
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
SELECT
	organisationunit.code, 
	max(datavalue.lastupdated) AS latest
FROM
	datavalue
	INNER JOIN
	organisationunit
	ON 
		datavalue.sourceid = organisationunit.organisationunitid
WHERE
	organisationunit.hierarchylevel = 3 AND
	datavalue.storedby NOT IN ('ryan','olavpo','chanyc') AND
	datavalue.dataelementid in (SELECT dataelementid FROM datasetelement wHERE datasetid =5047689)
GROUP BY
	organisationunit.code

sqlViews.name: MAL - IR Events
sqlViews.sqlQuery:
SELECT POrg.code, 'XX' as ISO2, organisationunit.code as ISO3, organisationunit.code as OrgUID, organisationunit.uid, programstage.name, programstageinstance.programstageid, programstage.uid as progStageUID, status, 
 POrg.code as ISOCode
FROM programstageinstance 
LEFT JOIN programstage ON (programstageinstance.programstageid = programstage.programstageid)
LEFT JOIN organisationunit ON (programstageinstance.organisationunitid = organisationunit.organisationunitid)
LEFT JOIN organisationunit as POrg ON (POrg.organisationunitid = organisationunit.parentid)
WHERE programstageinstance.created >= '2020.04.01' AND
programstageinstance.storedby <> 'fernandezl'
ORDER BY  POrg.code
